              "x": 0.35,
              "y": 0.35,
              "width": 0.35,
              "height": 0.5
            }
          },
          {
            "message": "Every debate runs for **[info]10 rounds[/info]**, alternating between your side and your opponent's. Whenever **[accent]it's your turn[/accent]**, choose the statement you believe will work best to win the favour of the moderator. If, along these 10 rounds, you will be more convincing than your opponent, you will **[success]win the debate[/success]**!",
            "modal": {
              "x": 0.35,
              "y": 0.35,
              "width": 0.35,
              "height": 0.5
            }
          },
